Move activity strings to own file
+ create gitignore
Use Logcat logging instead of console appender
- Add switch button for RelayType - Receive and unwrap buffered messages - other minor improvements
Use single button for connect / disconnect
Add progress bar, fix timeout when over cellular
Bind Hive2Hive and connect a H2HNode
Add Powertutor components + improve states at connection / login

finally add Powertutor components
+ fix wifi / 3g
Remove duplicate code and introduce BaseProgressTask
Show login button when accidentally went back to connection activity
Add context menu for deleting / opening files
Upload a file (using built-in file manager)
Introcuce own type representing the file tree (AndroidFile)
Upgrade to latest Android Studio and latest gradle version
Add first implementation of the FileEventListener
Don't generate credentials in UI thread
FileListener in UI Thread + connection fixes
Update file adapter anyway when event comes in
Own image for folder upload and deletion
Add action bar icons for refresh and upload
Add Powertutor | make map update configurable
Add Powertutor | make map update configurable
Use SpongyCastle for encryption / decryption. FST for serialization
Add images at login / connection screen + improve stability
Add shared folder icon and state
Open shared folder + update some strings
Warnings when delete / download failed + delete folder on 'sd card'
Memorize whether expert view is checked
Link GCM registration id with app version
Fix obtaining sender id from preferences
